01:18:00,000 --> 01:24:00,000
Let me explain the Scaffolder architecture.

15
01:24:00,000 --> 01:30:00,000
Backstage's Scaffolder has three layers.

16
01:30:00,000 --> 01:36:00,000
Layer one is the Developer Portal UI.
A form with fields like service name, team, traffic tier, database needed,
cache needed.

17
01:36:00,000 --> 01:42:00,000
Layer two is the Scaffolder Engine.
It executes steps defined in a template.yaml file.
Each step calls a built-in or custom action.

18
01:42:00,000 --> 01:48:00,000
Layer three is the external APIs.
GitHub API to create repositories and push files.
Kubernetes API to create ArgoCD applications.
Catalog API to register the new entity.

19
01:48:00,000 --> 01:54:00,000

20
01:54:00,000 --> 02:00:00,000
The template YAML defines what steps run, in what order, with what inputs.
The developer fills in the form. The engine executes.
The developer gets links to everything that was created.

21
02:00:00,000 --> 02:06:00,000

22
02:06:00,000 --> 02:12:00,000
First, let's install the required Scaffolder plugins.

23
02:12:00,000 --> 02:18:00,000
cd finops-idp.

24
02:18:00,000 --> 02:24:00,000
Add the GitHub scaffolder actions module.
yarn add at backstage slash plugin-scaffolder-backend-module-github.

25
02:24:00,000 --> 02:30:00,000
Add the Kubernetes actions module for creating ArgoCD apps.
yarn add at backstage slash plugin-scaffolder-backend-module-kubernetes.

26
02:30:00,000 --> 02:36:00,000
Add the AWS actions module for creating S3 buckets and tagging resources.
yarn add at backstage slash plugin-scaffolder-backend-module-aws.

27
02:36:00,000 --> 02:42:00,000
Add the ArgoCD plugin for the frontend and backend.
yarn add at roadiehq slash backstage-plugin-argo-cd.
yarn add at roadiehq slash backstage-plugin-argo-cd-backend.

28
02:42:00,000 --> 02:48:00,000

29
02:48:00,000 --> 02:54:00,000
Now register the modules in your backend.

30
02:54:00,000 --> 03:00:00,000
Open packages slash backend slash src slash index.ts.
Add imports for each plugin.

31
03:00:00,000 --> 03:06:00,000
backend.add for scaffolder-backend.
backend.add for scaffolder-backend-module-github.
backend.add for scaffolder-backend-module-kubernetes.
backend.add for scaffolder-backend-module-aws.

32
