03:48:00,000 --> 03:54:00,000

40
03:54:00,000 --> 04:00:00,000
First, the metadata.
apiVersion is scaffolder.backstage.io/v1beta3.
kind is Template.
name is microservice-finops.
title is Microservice with FinOps Optimized.

41
04:00:00,000 --> 04:06:00,000
description explains what this template does.
Creates a production-ready microservice with FinOps best practices built in.
Spot tolerations, resource requests by traffic tier, S3 lifecycle policy,
ArgoCD deployment, Kubecost cost attribution, and pre-deploy cost estimate.

42
04:06:00,000 --> 04:12:00,000
tags include Python, FastAPI, production, finops, and recommended.

43
04:12:00,000 --> 04:18:00,000

44
04:18:00,000 --> 04:24:00,000
